{
  "stem": "26765.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I did miss my-- my parents a lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then from there, Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Van Mackelenbergh picked us up one day and drove us to a little town called Eersel, where there was a convent with nuns.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was a home where-- children who are undernourished-- at that time, food was scarce.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Between the two world wars there was just nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If people had, you know, bread and butter, they were lucky.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so there were a lot of undernourished children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the government, in-- in conjunction with the Catholic Church or other religious organizations, had these homes where children came for a period of six weeks, mostly to gain weight.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, you know, to gain weight meant that you were healthy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To be heavy meant you were healthy-- a little different.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we were in this-- in this convent with-- I was with 100 girls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my brother was with about 100 Dutch boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Dutch children would come for a six-week period.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would eat a lot of good food-- rich food, very fatty-- so they would gain weight.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would go wandering in the woods every day and breathe fresh air, go to sleep very early, and nap in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and that lasted for six weeks for the Dutch children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But among those 200 Dutch children were about 50 Jewish children who were hidden there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of the 50, there were 45 who were half Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of the parents was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The other parent was Catholic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The half Jewish children were not sent to a concentration camp in Holland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of the 50 children, there were five of us who were Jewish on both sides of the family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My brother and I were two of the five.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
